    "Then:i) τ φ,d ≥ σ -1 ω. ii) If H φ,d ⊆ V ι = span{v 1,..., v ι }, then τ φ,d ≤ σ -1 ι. iii) For any d ≥ 1, the minimal value τ φ,d = σ -1 d is achieved when H φ,d = V d.Proposition 4 is due to Lemma 1 of [3] and Proposition 2 corresponds to part (iii)."
